        "short_description": "Clash with global players in this epic real-time strategy game!",
        "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are You Ready For A Real Fight?</h2><br>Brawl with 540 million players from all over the world! Lords Mobile is a real strategy game in the war time. In the game you can choose army troops and hero formations the way you want, create a badass city, make the best alliances to annihilate millions of enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/93042bbae2a41bd2e979a133f1b0c4e8.poster.avif?t=1753929753\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/93042bbae2a41bd2e979a133f1b0c4e8.webm?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/93042bbae2a41bd2e979a133f1b0c4e8.mp4?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Game Features]:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▶ ▶ Build Your Own Kingdom ◀◀</h2>Upgrade buildings, conduct research, train your troops, level your Heroes and lead your Kingdom well to prosper!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/402800953bc144b03ddb7a1eb1e576c2.poster.avif?t=1753929753\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/402800953bc144b03ddb7a1eb1e576c2.webm?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/402800953bc144b03ddb7a1eb1e576c2.mp4?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▶ ▶ Utilize Troop Formations ◀◀</h2>4 different troop types, and 6 different troop formations for you to choose from! Plan your lineups, take advantage of the counter system, and pair your troops with the right Heroes! Perfect your strategy to defeat your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/7fa23750689cc150bf94c6629de09843.poster.avif?t=1753929753\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/7fa23750689cc150bf94c6629de09843.webm?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/7fa23750689cc150bf94c6629de09843.mp4?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▶ ▶ Forge Alliances ◀◀</h2>Join a guild to fight alongside your allies! Ride into war together to conquer various exhilarating events.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/b8017d56cc52f8af694806a8f7e97bf8.poster.avif?t=1753929753\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/b8017d56cc52f8af694806a8f7e97bf8.webm?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/b8017d56cc52f8af694806a8f7e97bf8.mp4?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▶ ▶ Powerful Heroes Await ◀◀</h2>Create a strong team of 5 Heroes to fight through an RPG-style campaign! Let them lead your kingdom to glory as war generals!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/cd732471b7801183711a68f6f2d5752c.poster.avif?t=1753929753\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/cd732471b7801183711a68f6f2d5752c.webm?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041320/extras/cd732471b7801183711a68f6f2d5752c.mp4?t=1753929753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >===information===</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customer Service: <a href=\"mailto:Help.lordsmobile.steam@igg.com\">Help.lordsmobile.steam@igg.com</a></h2>",
